command chaining operation

four operators -- ; ,&&,||, && ||.
; -- semicolon // executes cmd2 regardless of success of failure of cmd1
&& -- logical AND cmd2 executes only after success of cmd1
|| -- logical OR cmd2 executes only after failure of cmd1

loops
for(cnt=0;cnt<10;cnt++)
do
  cmd1
  cmd2
done

-->to get 1 to 20 num we have cmd -- seq 1 20


